\c 1
\v 1 Mwakani wa kathatũ wa Njoakimu mũthamaki wa Njunda kwathana, Nebukadineca mũthamaki wa Babironi akĩthiĩ na akĩthiũrũrũkĩria Njerucaremu na Njeci yawe.\x - \xo 1:1 \xt 2Atham 24:1; 2Tene 36:5-7\x*
\v 2 Nawe Mwathani akĩnenkanĩra Njoakimu mũthamaki wa Njunda bamwe na into imwe cia ekarũ ya Ngai njarani cia Nebukandineca. nawe Nebukadineca agĩkuua into cia ekarũ ĩnu na agĩciĩbira nyombani ya mũthithũ wa ngai yawe. \x - \xo 1:2 \xt 2Atham 20:17,18; 24:10-16; 2Tene 36:10; Icaya 39:7,8\x*
\p
\v 3 Rĩu mũthamaki akĩatha Abinandaci, mũnene wa aruti wĩra mawe, alete antũ mamwe ma kuuma iciraeri marĩa ma-rĩ ma rũciaro rwa mũthamaki na ma rũciaro rũrĩa rwarĩ ĩgweta,
\v 4 na nthaka irĩa itĩna ũthũũku mwĩrĩni, irĩa mbega mũno, irĩa ciarĩ na ũũgĩ wa maũntũ mengĩ, irĩa nthomu na irĩa ikaũmba gũtungata nyomba ya mũthamaki. Agicioka akĩmwĩra amathomithie kĩthomo na rũthiomi rwa Kĩkarindea.
\v 5 Mũthamaki ũnu akĩathana manenkagĩrwe irio cia mũthamaki na ndibei ĩrĩa anyunyaga na akiuga matugwe ũgu gwa kabinda ka mĩaka ĩthatũ nĩ kenda yathira marũngame mbere ya mũthamaki.
\v 6 Gatagatĩ ka nthaka inu ma kuuma Njunda, nĩ kwarĩ na Ndanieri, Anania, Micaeri, na Acaia.
\v 7 Nawe mũnene wa aruti ma wĩra ma mũthamaki akĩmatuĩra mariĩtwa mangĩ. Agĩĩta Ndanieri Bericecaru, Anania akĩmwĩtwa Canderaci, Micaeri akĩmwĩta Micaci nawe Acaia akĩmwĩta Abendinego.
\v 8 Ĩndĩ Ndanieri agĩtua na nkoro yawe atĩ atĩthũkangia na kũrĩa irio cia mũthamaki, na atĩnyua ndibei ĩrĩa a-nyunyaga. Kwogu, akĩromba mũnene ũnu wa aruti ma wĩra amwĩtĩkĩrĩe atĩkethũkangie.
\v 9 Nawe Ngai agĩtũma Ndanieri etĩkĩrĩka na eguĩrwa kĩao methoni ma mũnene wa arutĩ ma wĩra ma mũthamaki.
\v 10 Ĩndĩ mũnene wa ũnu akĩĩra Ndanieri atĩrĩ, <<Nĩngũkĩra mũthamaki mũnene wakwa, ũrĩa athanĩte mũnenkerwe irio na gĩntũ gĩa kũnyua. Nĩkĩ abatiĩ kwona mothiũ menu marĩ mathũũku nkũrũki ya nthaka inu ciĩngĩ? Mũgaaca kũrũtha ũgu mũgakorwa mũtũmĩte ngĩe na thĩĩna.>>
\v 11Ĩndĩ ndanieri akĩĩra mũnene ũnu athurĩtwe nĩ kenda amenyerere ndanieri, anania, Micaeri, na Acaeria atĩrĩ,
\v 12 <<Ũinaanu geria ntungata ciaku gwa kabinda ka ntukũ ĩkũmi. Na ũtũgerie na kũrĩa ngano na rũncĩ rwa kũnyua.
\v 13 Thuubani ũcũũthe mothiũ metũ na mothiũ ma nthaka inu ciĩngĩ ikarĩa nyama na ũrũthĩre twiũ ntĩngata ciaku bũrĩa ũkenda.
