\c 2
\v 1 mwakani wa kaĩrĩ wa Nebukandineca kwathana, nĩ arotire kĩroto na nkoro yawe ikĩgĩa na kĩeba mũno na akĩremwa ni kũmaama.
\v 2 Nĩ ũntũ wogu, mũthamaki agiaiata aragũri, arogi, antũ ago, na aringi ma ciama nĩ kenda mamũtaũrĩre kĩroto kĩawe. namo makĩthiĩ mbere ya mũthamaki,
\v 3 Nawe mũthamaki akĩmeera atĩrĩ, <<Narotire kĩroto na nĩgĩkũnthĩnia mũno nĩ ũntũ ntĩkũmenya ũtaũku wakĩo.>>
\v 4 namo antũ mau makĩĩra mũthamaki na rũthiomi rwao atĩrĩ, <<Mũthamaki, ũrotũũra tene na tene! Ĩra ntungata ciaku kĩroto na tũkoona bũrĩa kĩgũtaũka.>>
\v 5 Mũthamaki akĩmaciokeria atĩrĩ, <<Nĩ ntuĩte ũntũ ũyũ : Mũkarega kũmbĩra kĩroto gĩakwa na ũtaũku wakĩo, mũkarengangwa icunce na nyomba cienu ithũkangue.
\v 6 Ĩndĩ ũkegua mũkambĩra kĩroto gĩakwa na mũgĩtaũre, nkamũnenkera ibeo, ibeo cia bata na nĩmũtĩithie. Rĩu mbĩrani kĩroto kĩu na mũntaũrĩre kĩo.>>
\v 7 Namo makĩmũciokeria atĩrĩ, <<Mũthamaki nĩ atwĩre kĩroto kĩawe natwi tũkĩna mũtaũrĩra kĩo.>>
\v 8 Mũthamaki akĩma iokeria rĩngĩ atĩrĩ, <<Nĩnkũmenya nama nĩka mũkũgeria kũũkia kabinda karaaca raaca nĩ ũntũ nĩ mũkũmenya nĩ ntuĩte ĩgamba rĩrĩ.
\v 9 Ũkegua mũtĩmbĩra kĩroto gĩakwa, mũrĩ na kĩberithio kĩmwe akĩ, nĩ ũntũ mũbangĩte kũmbĩĩra maũntũ ma ũrongo na maũntũ mathũũku ma kũmbĩtithia. Rĩu mbĩrani kĩroto gĩakwa nani nkamenya nwa mũbote kũgĩtaũra.>>
\v 10 Aringi ciama mau makĩĩra mũthamaki atĩirĩ, << Gũtĩ mũntũ nwarĩ ũrĩkũ nthĩ ĩno ũnkĩrũtha bũu mũthamaki akwenda. na gũtĩ na mũthamaki nwarĩ ũmwe, kana mũnene nwarĩ ũmwe akĩĩra mũrogi, mũntũ mũgo kana mũragũri arũthe ũntũ ta ũnu.
\v 11 Nĩ ũntũ wa magegania ũyũ mũthamaki akwenda na gũtĩ mũntũ ũnkĩũmba kũmwonia ũntũ ũnu tiga ngai irĩa itĩkaranagia bamwe na antũ.>>
\v 12 Ũntũ ũnu ũgĩtũma mũthamaki athũũra mũno athũũre mũno na akĩruta watho na akiuga antũ marĩa aũgĩ monthe ma Babironi nĩ maũragwe.
\v 13 Kwogu watho ũnu ũgĩtangacwa na antũ marĩa aũgĩ marĩ bakubĩ kũũragwa, makĩthiĩ gũceria Ndanieri na arata mawe nĩ kenda maũragwe.
\p
\v 14 Nĩrĩo Ndanieri a-rĩria na Arioci na ũũgĩ mwĩngĩ. Arioci a-rĩ mũnene wa athingari ma mũthamaki nawe e-ndaga kũũraga antũ monthe aũgĩ marĩa ma-tũũraga Babironi.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt Icaya 34:5-17; 63:1-6; Njer 49:7-22; Ecek 25:12-14; 35:1-15; Amoci 1:11,12; Maraki 1:2-5\x*
\v 15 Ndanieri akĩũria Arioci atĩrĩ, << Nĩkĩ mũthamaki a-rutite watho mũthũũku ta ũyũ? Nĩrĩo Arioci amũ-taarĩrĩrie maũntũ monthe marĩa me-karĩkĩte.
\v 16 Kwogu Ndanieri akĩthiĩ nyombani ya mũthamaki, na akĩmũũria amũnenkera kabinda kaniini nĩ kenda amwĩra ũtaũku wa kĩroto kĩawe.
\p
\v 17 Thuubani, Ndanieri agĩcioka nyombani yawe na agĩtaarĩrĩria arata mawe tamo Anania, Mishaeri, na Acaria maũntũ monthe marĩa me-karĩkĩte.
\v 18 A-merire maũntũ mau nĩ kenda maboye Ngai, Ũrĩa Ũtũũraga Ĩgũrũ amataũrĩre kĩrĩga kĩu. Na rĩngĩ, nĩ kenda mo matĩkaũragwe bamwe na antũ monthe aũgĩ marĩa ma-tũũraga Babironi.
\v 19 Ũtukũ ũnu, Ndanieri akĩguũrĩrwa ũtaũku wa kĩroto kĩa mũthamaki kĩonekini. Nawe Ndanieri agĩkumia Ngai ũrĩa Ũtũũraga Ĩgũrũ.
\v 20 Ndanieri akiuga atĩrĩ, << Kumiani riĩtwa rĩa Ngai tene na tene nĩ ũntũ ũũgĩ na binya nĩ ciawe.
\v 21 We agarũrũga mabinda na ciathi. Anenkagĩra athamaki wathani na agacuna mangĩ u, agacioka akanenkera marĩa aũgĩ ũũgĩ na akanenkera antũ marĩa marĩ na ũmenyo ũtaũku.
\v 22 Ngai aguũragĩria antũ irĩga na mbithu. We amenyaga maũntũ marĩa mabithe. Na werũ ũtũũranagia nawe.
\v 23 Nĩ ngũgũciokeria nkatho na ngagũkumia weũ Ngai wa macucu makwa, nĩ ũntũ wa kũnenkera ũũgĩ na ũboti. Nĩũmenyithĩtie maũntũ marĩa tũrendaga kũmenya nĩ ũntũ nũtũguũrĩrĩtie kĩroto kĩa mũthamaki.
\v 24 Rĩu Ndanieri akĩthiĩ kũrĩ Arioki, ũrĩa athuurĩwe nĩ mũthamaki aũrage antũ marĩa aũgĩ ma babironi na akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, <<Ũtĩkaũrage antũ marĩ aũgĩ ma Babironi. Mbira mbere ya Mũthamaki nĩ kenda nĩmwĩra kĩroto kĩawe na nĩ mũrtaũrĩra.
\v 25 nawe Arioki akĩbira Ndanieri kũrĩ mũthamaki na akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, <<Nkwona mũntũ ũrĩa ũnkĩumba kuuga na gũtaũra kĩroto gĩaku gatagatĩni ka antũ marĩa matabĩtwe kuuma Njunda.>>
\v 26 Kwogu mũthamaki akĩũria Ndanieri (ũrĩa wetagwa Berigeca) atĩrĩ <<nwa ũbote kũmbĩra na gũtaũra kĩroto gĩakwa?
\v 27 Ndanieri akĩmũciokeria atĩrĩ <<Gũtĩ mũntũ mũũgĩ, mũrogi, kana mũragũri ũnkĩbota kwĩra mũthamaki mbithũ ĩnu,
\v 28 ĩndĩ kũrĩ na Ngai ĩgũrũ ũrĩa ũtaũraga mbithũ. Na nĩ aguũrĩrĩtie mũthamaki Nebukandineca bũrĩa maũntũ marĩa magekarĩka ntukũni ciĩcĩte. Kĩroto gĩaku na cioneki irĩa wonire ũrĩ gĩtandani gĩaku nĩ ino,
\p
\v 29 Rĩrĩa weũ, mũthamaki, wamamiĩ gĩtandani gĩaku, nĩ wa-rotire bwa maũntũ marĩa magekarĩka bĩndĩ ĩgaaca, na Ngai, ũrĩa ũguũragĩria antũ iriga, agĩkuguũrĩria maũntũ mama.
\v 30 Gĩtũmi kĩrĩa Ngai anguũrĩrie kĩriga gĩkĩ tĩ ũntũ nĩ mũũgĩ nkũrũki ya antũ marĩa mangĩ, ĩndĩ Ngai arũthire ũgu nĩ kenda weũ mũthamaki ũmenye ũtaũku wa marĩa weciririe bwamo.
\v 31 Kĩrotoni nĩ wonire yũmba ĩnene mbere yaku. Yũmba rĩu rĩarĩ na werũ mũnene mũno na rĩarũngamĩte mbere yaku na nĩrĩamkaknagia mũno.
\v 32 Kĩongo kĩa yũmba rĩu kĩarĩ kĩa thaabu ntherie, kĩthũri na njara cia rĩo ciarĩ cia betha, nda na kĩũno kĩarĩo ciarĩ cia gĩcango.
\v 33 Magũrũ ma yũmba rĩu marĩ ma cuma na matende marĩo marĩ ma cuma nuthu na ntaka nũthu.
\v 34 Na ũcũthĩte, ũkĩona ĩbiga rĩagerwa na ũtĩkwona njra irĩa cia rĩgerire. Narĩa ĩbiga rĩu rĩkĩringa yũmbo rĩu magũrũni marĩo marĩ ma cũma na ntaka, na yũmbo rĩu rĩkiunĩkanga tũcunce.
\v 35 Na cuma ĩnu, ntaka ĩnu, betha ĩnu, gĩcango kĩu, na thaabu ĩnu ikiunĩkanga icunce na igĩkarar ta magoko marĩa ma-rĩ rwarani bĩndĩ ya kũthia ngano. naru rũkũngi rũkĩmaburuta na makĩrega kwonekana rĩngĩ narĩo ĩbiga rĩrĩa rĩaringire yũmbo rĩu rĩgĩtuĩka kĩrĩma kĩnene na rĩgĩcũra nthĩ.
\v 36 Wonire maũntũ mau kĩrotoni gĩaku na nĩngũgũtaũrĩra kĩo.
\v 37 Weũ mũthamaki, ũrĩ mũthamaki mũnene na Ngai wa ĩgũrũ nĩ akũnenkerete ũthamaki na binya na gĩtĩĩo,
\v 38 Ngai agwĩtĩkĩrĩrĩtie wathe antũ monthe, nyamũ cionthe irĩa itũũraga nthĩ na icici cionthe cia rerani. Akũthuurĩte wathage into inu cionthe na weũ nĩ kĩongo kĩu kĩa thaabu.
\v 39 Rĩrĩ ũgakua, kũgaũkĩrĩra ũthamaki ũngĩ ũrĩa ũtĩna binya tĩ waku, na ũthamaki ũngĩ wa kathatũ wa gĩcango ũrĩa ũkaathaga nthĩ yonthe.
\v 40 Na gũkegua kũrĩ na ũthamaki wa kana ũrĩa ũkegua wĩkari ta cuma nĩ ũntũ cuma yunangaga into cionthe na igaciĩcinda, ũgũ nĩ tabu ũthamaki ũnu ũkaunanga mĩgongo ĩnu ĩngĩ ĩtuĩke tũcunce.
\v 41 Na watabũrĩa wonire matende magaũkanĩte cuma na ntaka, ũgũ nĩbu ũthamaki ũnu ũkegua ũgaũkanĩte. Ũkegua ũrĩ na binya ta cuma na kũngĩ ũti` na binya ta ntaka wa ta ũgu wonire cuma ĩbu njanĩtue na ntaka.
\v 42 Ciara cia matende mau ciarĩ nũthu cuma na nuthu ntaka, kwogu ũthamaki ũnu ũkegua ũgaũkanĩte na ũtĩgũ ũrĩ na binya.
\v 43 na wa ta ũgu wonire cuma ĩbu njanĩtue na ntaka, nwa tabu makegua mebu njanĩtie na antũ ĩndĩ matĩambatana ta bũrĩa cuma na ntaka itĩnkĩũmba kwambatana.
\v 44 Bĩndĩ ĩrĩa athamaki mau makegua makĩatha nhtĩ, Ngai akarũngamia ũthamaki ũrĩa ũtĩkarothũkangua tene na tene na antũ mangĩ matĩũmba kũũbota. Ĩndĩ ũthamaki ũnu ũkathiria mothamaki mau mangĩ na ũgatũũra tene na tene.
\v 45 Na wa ta ũgu wonire ĩbiga rĩekua ũtĩkwona njara, na rĩaunanga yũmba rĩu rĩarĩ na thaabu, betha, gĩcango, cuma na ntaka, ũgũ nwabu Ngai mũnene akwonirie maũntũ marĩa magekarĩka bĩndĩ ĩgaaca. Kĩroto kĩu nĩ kĩama na rĩu nĩ ũmenyete ũtaũku wakĩo.>>
\v 46 Rĩu Nebukandineca egua ũgu, akĩgwa nthĩ magũrũni mawe na agĩtĩithia ndanieri. Akĩruta watho wa kuuga ndanieri arũtĩrwe kĩgongwana kĩrĩ na mũtararĩ.
\v 47 Na akĩĩra ndanieri atĩrĩ, <<Nama ngai wenu nĩwe Ngai wa ngai cionthe, na ngai wa athamaki ũrĩ arĩ na ũboti wa kũguũria mbithũ nĩ ũntũ nĩ aũmbire gũkũguũrĩria kĩriga kĩu.
\v 48 Kwogu mũthamaki agĩtuga Ndanieri, akĩmũnenkera iboe na akĩmũtua mũnene wa anene monthe ma Babironi na mũnene wa antũ monthe aũgĩ.
\v 49 Na Ndanieri akĩromba mũthamaki atũme Candiraka, meceki na Abendinego matuĩke antongoria ma Babironi. Ndanieri atũũraga nyombani ya mũthamaki.
\c 3
\v 1 Mũthamaki Nebukandineca akĩthontheka mũbianano wa thaabu, ũrĩa wa-rĩ na ũraaca wa mĩkono ĩthanthatũ na wariĩ wa mĩkono ĩthanthatũ. Na akĩwĩrũngamia Ndura gĩcigoni kĩa Babironi.
\v 2 Na mũthamaki agĩĩta anene, arũngamĩrĩri, athani, ataarani, arũngamĩrĩri ma mũthithũ, acirithania, acirithania na anene mau mangĩ monthe ma gĩcigo kĩu, mathiĩ makarugũrie mũbuanano ũnu Mũthamaki Nebukandineca a-rũngamĩtie.
\v 3 Athani, arũngamĩrĩri, atongoria, ataarani, arũngamĩrĩri ma mũthithũ, acirithania, acirithania na anene mangĩ ma gĩcigo kĩu, monthe magĩtũngana nĩ kenda marugũria mũbuanano ũnu Mũthamaki Nebukandineca a-rũthĩte na makĩrũngama mbere ya mũbianano ũnu.
\v 4 Nawe mũntũ wa kũbuuba karumbeta na akĩanĩrĩra akiugaga atĩrĩ, <<Mwiũ antũ ma mĩgongo yonthe, na nthĩ cionthe na nthiomi cionthe mwathĩtwe mũrũthe bũbũ,
\v 5 rĩrĩa mũkegua mũgambo wa karumbeta, na biringi, na mĩtũũrirũ na wandindi cia ndigi mĩngĩ, na mĩthemba mĩngĩ ya ithembe, wa mũntũ enamĩrĩre na kũthathaia mũbũanano ũnu wa thaabu ũrĩa mũthamaki Nebũkandineca arũngamĩtie.
\v 6 Mũntũ wonthe ũrĩa wonthe ũkarega kwĩnamĩrĩra awĩthathaia, akagerwa ĩcamarĩroni rĩa mwanki mũnene.>>
\v 7 Kwogu rĩrĩa antũ mau ma kuuma mĩgongo mĩngĩ na ma-ragia nthiomi ciĩngĩ me-guire mĩgambo ya ngoci, ya mĩtũrirũ, ya wandĩndĩ ya ndigi mĩ̃ngĩ, ya wandĩndĩ ya ndigi mĩngĩ, na ya into cia kwina ciĩngĩ, makĩĩnamĩrĩra mũbũanano ũnu na makĩwĩthathaia.
\v 8 Kabindani kau, Akarindea mamwe makĩthiĩ na makĩthitanga Ayaundi.
\v 9 Makĩĩra Mũthamaki Nebukandineca atĩrĩ, <<Weũ mũthamaki, ũrotũũra tene na tene!
\v 10 Weũ, mũthamaki, wa-rutire watho atĩ antũ monthe marĩa makegua mũgambo wa tarumbeta, wa mĩtũrirũ, wa wandĩndĩ, wa ithembe mĩngĩ, na wa into cia kwina ciĩngĩ nwa nkinya enamĩrĩre mũbuanano na awĩthathaie
\v 11 na ũrĩa wonthe ũtĩkawĩnamĩrĩra na awĩthathaie, akagerwa ĩcamarĩro rĩa mwanki mũnene.
\v 12 Ĩndĩ kũrĩ na Ayaundi mamwe marĩa ũtuĩte arũngamĩrĩri ma wĩra wa kũu Babĩroni tamo Candiraka, Mĩceki na Abendendego, marĩa matĩgũgũtĩa weũ Mũthamaki. Matĩgũtungatĩra ngai ciaku kana mathathaia mũbuanano wa thaabu ũrĩa ũrũngamĩtie.>>
\v 13 Nĩ ũntũ wogu, Nebukandineca akĩth`ũura na akĩruta watho na marakara, akiuga Candiraka, Miceki na Abendinego. Namo makĩbirwa mbere ya mũthamaki.
\v 14 Nawe akĩmaũria atĩrĩ, <<Mwiũ candiraka, Mĩceki na Abendinego mũtĩtungatĩra ngai ciakwa kana mũtungata mũbuanano wa thaabu ũrĩa ndũngamĩtie?
\v 15 Rĩrĩa rĩngĩ mũkegua mĩgambo ya tũrumbeta, mĩtũrirũ, wandĩndĩ na ithembe bamwe na mĩthemba yonthe ya mĩtũrirũ, mwĩnamĩrĩrie na mũthathaie mũbuanano ũnu nthondekete, bũu nĩ bwega. Ĩndĩ mwarega kũwĩthathaia, mũkagerwa mwankini mũnene. Nĩ ngai ũnkĩũmba kũmũbonokia kuuma njarani ciakwa?>>
\v 16 Candiraka, Mĩceki na Abendendego magĩciokeria mũthamaki atĩrĩ, <<Weũ Nebukandineca, tũtĩteterera mbere yaku ũntũni ũyũ.
\v 17 Ũkethĩrwa tũkagerwa mwankini mũnene, Ngai ũrĩa tũtungataga nwa agatũbonokie kuuma mwankini ũnu, na atũbonokie kuuma njarani ciaku.
\v 18 Ĩndĩ ũkethĩrwa atĩtũbonokia, nĩtũkwenda ũmenye atĩ, tũtĩtungata ngai ciaku kana tũthathaia mũbuanano wa thaabu ũrĩa ũrũthĩte.>>
\v 19 Rĩu Nebukandineca akĩthũũra mũno nĩ Candiraka, Meceki, na Abendinego na agĩcĩncia meciria mawe nĩ ũntũ wogu. Kwogu akĩatha ntungata ciawe itũme mwanki ũtuĩka mũnene mũno.
\v 20 Agĩcioka akĩatha athigari mamwe mawe marĩa marĩ na binya mũno mobe Candiraka, Mĩceki, na Abendendegao, na mamagere mwankini mũnene.
\v 21 Kwogu antũ mau maĩrĩ makĩambatwa na makĩgerwa mwankini mũnene mekĩrĩte tũbuuti, tũkonyo, nguo cia ũthamaki na mobetwe na mĩkanda.
\v 22 Mwanki ũnu ũkĩũraga athigari marĩa ma-gerire Candiraka, Meceki, na Abendinego mwankini nĩ ũntũ mwanki ũnu wa-rĩ mũnene mũno na nĩ ũntũ ma-thĩkĩrĩte mũthamaki na karũgĩ mũno.
\v 23 Kwogu Candiraka, Mecaka, na Abendinego makĩgwa mwankini mũnene mũno. Mo-betwe na mĩkanda na binya.
\v 24 Rĩu Mũthamaki Nebanekondemaci akĩrigara mũno, akĩrũngama na karũgĩ na akĩũria ataarani mawe atĩrĩ, <<Anga tĩ antũ mathatũ twĩkirie mwankini? / Namo ataarani makĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ, <<Nĩma, mũthamaki.>>
\v 25 Mũthamaki akiuga atĩrĩ, <<Ta cũũthĩrĩriani! Nĩmona antũ mana magendererete mwankini, matĩobetwe kana megũrũka, na mũntũ wa kana onekaga ta mwana wa ngai.>>
\v 26 Nebukandineca akĩthiĩ mũrangoni wa mwanki mũnene mũno. Na akiugĩrĩria, <<Candiraka, Meceki, na Abendinego, ntungata cia Ngai Ũrĩa Ũrĩ Ĩgũrũ Mũno, umani! Ncũni baba!>> Kwogu Candiraka, Meceki, na Abendinego makiuma kuuma mwankini.
\v 27 Namo athani, arũngamĩrĩri, aathani na ataarani magĩtũngana mamathiũrũrũkĩrĩtie. Na makĩona mwanki ũtarĩ ũkũthũũkia mĩĩrĩ yao, kana njuĩrĩ cia ciongo ciao ibĩa, nacio ncũng'ua ciao ita-bĩa na mĩĩrĩ yao ĩta-nunkaga ntoogo.
\v 28 Nebukandineca akiuga atĩrĩ, <<Nĩ ngũkumia Ngai ũrĩa Candiraka, Meceki, na Abendinego marutagĩra wĩra. Ngai a-tũmire mũraika nĩ kenda abonokia antũ mama! Antũ mama metĩkĩtie Ngai na matarũtha maũntũ monthe marĩa mbugire. Mararĩ na wendi gũkua nĩ kenda matĩĩa Ngai wao bantũ ba kũrutĩra ngai ciĩngĩ wĩra na bantũ ba kũthathaia ngai ciĩngĩ.
\v 29 Kwogu nathana atĩ antũ ma mũgongo nwarĩ ũrĩkũ kana rũthiomi rũrĩkũ, marĩa makaaria ũntũ mũgeni ĩgũrũ rĩa Ngai wa Canderaki, Mĩceki na Abendendego, maunangwe icunce, na nyomba ciao ituĩwe ikundi cia ncũng'ua, nĩ ũntũ gũtĩ ngai ĩngĩ ĩnkĩbota kũbonokia antũ.>>
\v 30 Mũthamaki agĩtũma Candiraka, Meceki, na Abendinego matuĩka atongoria anene mũno gĩcigoni gĩetagwa Babironi.
