\c 7
\v 1 Mwaka wa mbere wa mũthamaki Bericaca kwatha Babironi, ndanieri nĩ agĩĩre na kĩroto na akĩonua kĩoneki amamiĩ gĩtandani kĩawe. Kwogu akĩandĩka kĩroto kĩu na maũntũ marĩa monthe onire kĩrotoni.
\v 2 Ndanieri akĩandĩka na akiuga, <<Nonirue kĩoneki ũtukũ. Nacũũthire na nkĩona nkũngi inya cia ĩgũrũ ikĩburuta na binya mũno kũu ĩriani.
\v 3 Nyamũ inya cia mĩthemba nkũrani igĩcioka ikiumĩra kuuma ĩriani.\x - \xo 7:3 \xt Kũg 13:1; 17:8\x*
\v 4 Nyamũ ya mbee yekari ta ciimba na ĩrĩ na mathagu maĩrĩ ta rwĩgĩ, na namĩcũũtha mathagu mayo makĩgũũka guoya na ĩgĩukĩrĩrua kuuma nthĩ ĩkĩnarũngamua na magũrũ maĩrĩ ta mũntũ, na ĩgĩcioka yanenkerwa nkoro ya mũntũ. \x - \xo 7:4 \xt Kũg 13:2\x*
\v 5 Ngĩcioka nkĩona nyamũ ya kaĩrĩ mbere yakwa. Nyamũ ĩnu yekari ta nduba. Nayo ĩgĩũkĩrĩrua mwena ũmwe na kanyua kayo nĩ karĩ na mĩbĩndĩ ĩthatũ magegoni, na makĩĩra nyamũ ĩnu atĩrĩ, <<Ũkĩra ũrĩe nyama.>>
\v 6 Ngĩcũũtha na nkĩona nyamũ ĩngĩ mbere yakwa. Nyamũ ĩnu yekari ta nyoroco na ya-rĩ na mathagu mana ta ma gĩcici mũgongoni wayo. Nyamũ ĩnu ya-rĩ na ciongo inya na ĩkĩnenkerwa wathani.
\v 7 Thuubani nkĩona nyamũ ya kana ĩrĩ mbere yakwa kĩonekini gĩa ũtukũ. Nyamũ ĩnu nĩ yamakanagia mũno, ya-rĩ na binya na nĩ ya-rĩ na ũboti mwĩngĩ mũno na ĩrĩna magego ma cuma manene mũno. yarĩre na ĩkiunanga icunce na ĩgĩkinyanga into irĩa yatiarĩtie. Ya-rĩ nyamũ ya mwanya mũno kũrĩ inu ciĩngĩ ithatũ nĩ ũntũ nĩ ya-ri na ngoci ĩkumi.\x - \xo 7:7 \xt Kũg 12:3; 13:1\x*
\v 8 Rĩrĩa neciaragia ĩgũrũ rĩa ngoci inu, nkĩona rũgoci rũngĩ mbere yakwa. Rũgoci rũuu rwarĩ rũniini na rwakũrire gatagatĩ ka ngoci inu ciĩngĩ na na mũthiani wa ngoci ĩnu, kũgĩcinũrwa ngoci ithatũ. mũthia wa ngoci inu nĩ kwarĩ na metho ta mũntũ na kanyua karĩa kanagĩrĩra ciugo.\x - \xo 7:8 \xt Kũg 13:5,6\x*
\v 9 Nkĩona itĩ cia nũnene cia retwa na mũntũ ũmwe ũrĩa wa-rĩ mũkũrũ wa bĩndĩ ĩnu agĩkara nthĩ. Ekĩrĩte nguo irĩa njerũ ta mbarabu, na njuĩrĩ cia kĩongo` kĩawe ciarĩ ta guoya ntherie. Gĩtĩ kĩawe kĩa ũnene kĩathiũrũrũkĩrĩtue nĩ mwanki na kĩarĩ na magũrũ marĩ na mwanki wakanaga.\x - \xo 7:9 a \xt Kũg 20:4; \xo b \xt Kũg 1:14\x*
\v 10 Mũburo wa mwanki ũkĩgenda mbere yawe na antũ magiri makĩmũtungata, na mangĩ magiri mengĩ makĩrũngama mbere yawe. Mbuku ikĩrugũrwa na antũ magĩtuĩrwa.\x - \xo 7:10 a \xt Kũg 5:11; \xo b \xt Kũg 20:12\x*
\v 11 Ngĩcũũtha kabinda kau na nĩ ũntũ wa mũgambo mũnene na ciugo nene irĩa nyamũ ĩnu yaugĩte, ikĩũragw na mwĩrĩ wayo ũkĩthũkangua, ĩgĩocwa na ĩgĩkua mwankini.
\v 12 Nyamũ inu ciĩngĩ igĩcunwa wathani wacio ĩndĩ igĩtĩkĩrĩrua gũtũũra.
\v 13 Ngĩcũũtha kĩonekini gĩakwa gĩa ũtukũ na nkĩona mũntũ ũmwe ũrĩa wekari ta mwana wa mũntũ acĩĩte bamwe na matũ ma ĩgũrũ na agĩkubĩbĩrĩria mũkũrũ ũnu ekarĩrĩte gĩtĩ kĩa ũnene.\x - \xo 7:13 \xt Math 24:30; 26:64; Mko 13:26; 14:62; Ruka 21:27; Kũg 1:7,13; 14:14\x*
\v 14 Nawe akĩnenkerwa wathani na ũnene na ũthamaki nĩ kenda antũ ma mĩgo`ngo yonthe na nthĩ cionthe na nthiomi cionthe mamũtungatire tene na tene. wathani wawe ni wa tene na tene na ũtĩkaro botwa naũtĩkaro thira kana ũthũkangua.\x - \xo 7:14 \xt Kũg 11:15\x*
\v 15 <<Niũ, Ndanieri, nĩ na-gĩĩre na kĩeba nkoroni yakwa, na kĩoneki kĩu gĩa kabinda karaaca gĩkĩnthĩĩnia mũno.
\v 16 Ngĩkubĩrĩrĩria ũmwe wa antũ marĩa ma-rĩ bakubĩ na ũma wa maũntũ mau monthe. Na akĩmbĩra ũtaũku wa maũntũ mau monthe.
\v 17 Nyamũ inu inya nkũrani nĩ athamaki mana marĩa magaaca nthĩ.
\v 18 \x - \xo 7:18 \xt Kũg 22:5\x*
\v 19 Na nkĩenda kũmenya ũtauku wa nyamũ ya kana ĩrĩa ya-rĩ kũraca na irĩa cii`ngĩ na yamakanaggia mũno ĩrĩ na magego ma cuma na nkũnyũ cia gĩcango. Nyamũ ĩrĩa ya rĩire na kuunanga irĩa ciatigarire tũcunce.
\v 20 Na nkĩenda kũmenya maũntũ makoniĩ ngoci ĩkũmi ĩrĩa ciarĩ kĩongoni kĩayo, bamwe na ngoci ĩnu ĩngi ĩrĩa yakũrire gatagatĩ gacio ĩrĩ na ngoci ithatũ na metho na kanyua na ĩrĩ na mũkũrani na ngoci inu ciĩngĩ.
\v 21Rĩrĩa na-thiĩte na mbere gũcũũthĩrĩria, nkĩona ngoci ĩno ĩkĩrũa na antũ ma Ngai na ĩkĩmaboota. \x - \xo 7:21 \xt Kũg 13:7\x*
\v 22 Na agĩĩca mũkũrũ ũnu bamwe na atheru mawe na akĩmatuĩra. Na bĩndĩ ĩnu atheru makĩgwatĩra ũthamaki.\x - \xo 7:22 \xt Kũg 20:4\x*
\v 23 na akiuga ũũ, <Nyamũ ĩnu ya kana ũkegua ũrĩ ũthamaki wa kana nthĩ, na ũkegua ũrĩ baraaca na mothamaki mau mangĩ, nau ũkarĩa nthĩ yonthe na ũmĩkinyange na ũmiunange tũcunce.
\v 24 Nacio ngoci irĩa ĩkũmi nĩ athamaki ĩkũmi marĩa magaaca ũthamakini ũnu na mathiĩ, na ũngĩ agaũkĩrĩra thuuba yao ũrĩa agakorwa arĩ baraaca namo, nawe akagwithia athamaki mathatũ.\x - \xo 7:24 \xt Kũg 17:12\x*
\v 25 Akaragia maũntũ ma kũregana na Ũrĩa Ũrĩ Ĩgũrũ Mũno, na akanyarira antũ ma Ngai, na ageria kũgarũra mabinda na watho. Namo antũ ma Ngai makagũrwa ruungu rwa wathani wawe gwa kabinda, mabinda maĩrĩ, na nuthu ya kabinda.\x - \xo 7:25 \xt Kũg 12:14; 13:5,6\x*
\v 26 Ĩndĩ gooti agacirithua, na wathani wawe ũkathirua tene na tene.
\v 27 Na wathani a mothamaki monthe ma nthĩ ũkanenkerwa antũ ma Mwathani marĩa makegua marĩ na ũtheru. Ũthamaki wa Mwathani ũkegua ũrĩ bo tene na tene, na athamaki mau monthe makamũthathaia na monthe makamwathĩkagĩra.>> \x - \xo 7:27 a \xt Kũg 20:4; \xo b \xt Kũg 22:5\x*
\v 28 Ũnu nĩu m`uthia wa ũntũ ũnu. Nani ndanieri, meciria makwa makĩnthĩnia na ũthiũ wakwa uk`igarũrũka, ĩndĩ nkiiga ũntũ ũnu nkoroni yakwa.
